<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/731505-in-the-end-why-is-sara-back-in-the">In the end why is Sara back in the beggining of the book? Why and how did that happen .</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_731505'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13436345-amber-house">like</a></span>

