<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/492537-does-anyone-know-why-this-book-and-its">Does anyone know why this book and its sequel seem to have disappeared from all the online stores ? I was looking to see if book Three was out and not only was it not but the other two books seem to no longer be for sale either. What gives ? ?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_492537'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13436345-amber-house">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/492537-does-anyone-know-why-this-book-and-its">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/492537-does-anyone-know-why-this-book-and-its">Add your answer</a>
</li>
